high_descs: Turn left and walk toward the wall, then turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the egg that is in front of the sink.
Turn right and walk toward the wall, then turn right to face the fridge.
Cool the egg inside the fridge and take it out.
Turn right, walk forward, and turn left to face the counter.
Place the egg on the counter in front of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold egg on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the egg sitting on the left side of the sink, behind the sponge.
Turn right and walk towards the door.  Then turn to the right to face the fridge near the door.

Open the bottom door of the fridge, place the egg on the middle shelf to the left of the potato.  Close the door and wait a few seconds.  Open the door, take the egg back out, and close the fridge door.
Holding the egg, move to the counter that is on the immediate right of the fridge.
Put the egg in the middle of the counter in front of the knife that is nearer the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg onto the counter by the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the left side of the sink that will be on your right.,
Pick up the egg that's on the left side of the sink.
Turn right until you are even with the fridge on your right and then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Put the egg in the fridge and close the door and let it cool off then get it back out and close the fridge.
Take two steps to your right so you are looking at the counter to the left of the stove.
Put the egg near the edge of the counter under the tomato and slightly to the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold egg on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right in front of the sink.
Pick up the brown egg on the left side of the sink closest to the lettuce.
Turn right then walk towards the door, hang a right, walk towards the refrigerator.
Open refrigerator door and place the brown egg on the second shelf then close the door. Open the door and pick up the brown egg on the second shelf then close the door.
Turn right and walk towards the stove, then turn left in front of the counter top.
Place the brown egg on the counter top on the left side of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a brown egg on a counter top located near a stove.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink.
Pick up the egg to the left of the sink.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Chill the egg and take it out again.
Turn right and approach the stove.
Put the egg on the counter to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold egg on the counter.
